						<div class="postbody">You need to find the color you want in the NES global palette.<br /><br /><!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="http://nesdev.com/nespalette.zip">http://nesdev.com/nespalette.zip</a><!-- m --><br /><br />NES does not use a RGB system for colors. Find the color and it's value in the file linked above.<br /><br />You can program NES games in C, others have done it. It could work out reasonably well.</div>

