				<tr>
					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">You need to write the palette at $3F00 if you want that to be the &quot;clear screen&quot; color. This color index is mirrored at $3F04, 08,0C and at 14,18, and 1C. If you are writing $3F02, you're just setting a background tile color. Not the color it uses when there is no BG or Sprite pixel to be drawn, aka the clear color.</div>

